msgid "Ah... here it is."
msgstr "ああ……あった。"

msgid "I suppose these cursed doors must be fairly common."
msgstr "この呪いの扉、ずいぶん色んな所にあるんだね。"

msgid "Not that common. And they kinda suck."
msgstr "それほどじゃないぜ。それに、ちょっと悪質だ。"

msgid "Sometimes you get stuck with no way to go back."
msgstr "時々、戻れなくなって詰むんだよ。"

msgid "I see."
msgstr "へえ。"

msgid "So it's a dead end after all."
msgstr "じゃあ、やっぱり行き止まりなんだ。"

msgid "Since there's no doorknobs here..."
msgstr "ドアノブがついてないし……"

msgid "Looks like it."
msgstr "みたいだな。"

msgid "An empty slot."
msgstr "何も挿さっていない穴。"

msgid "Place a doorknob?"
msgstr "ドアノブを挿す？"

msgid "Gray Doorknob"
msgstr "灰色のドアノブ"

msgid "White Doorknob"
msgstr "白いドアノブ"

msgid "Return Doorknob"
msgstr "帰還のドアノブ"

msgid "Do not"
msgstr "やめておく"

msgid "I guess it's finally time to use this."
msgstr "ついにこれを使う時が来たみたい。"
